                        <p><span class="font-semibold dark:text-gray-100">Concepts:</span> Machine Learning, REST APIs, Data Visualization, CRM Development, Responsive Design</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Download Resume -->
                <div class="mt-8 w-full">
                    <a href="/resume.pdf" download class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors">
                        📄 Download Resume (PDF)
